Class MorseCodeTree

java.lang.Object
MorseCodeTree
All Implemented Interfaces:
LinkedConverterTreeInterface<java.lang.String>
public class MorseCodeTree
extends java.lang.Object
implements LinkedConverterTreeInterface<java.lang.String>
This class is a generic linked binary tree which inherits from the LinkedConverterTreeInterface The class uses an external generic TreeNode class paramaterized as a String: TreeNode This class uses the private member of root. Nodes are added based on their morse code value.
